data.text:
Chicago Bulls' John Lucas III, right, talks with Houston Texans' Andre Johnson during halftime of the Houston Lockout Celebrity Basketball Game hosted by former player and coach John Lucas on Sunday, Nov. 20, 2011, in Houston. Several NBA players took part in the event that will benefit charities including the John Lucas Foundation, which helps athletes who need after care or wellness services and programs. (AP Photo/David J. Phillip)
